_sText: Welcome to the Map I tried my best on. There are some issues with the lighting like how it's very noticeable on the wall but it doesn't hurt the map itself. Contact me on my Steam profile "SlayAChicken" or on here if you fine any issues with the map. This is a short but the longest map I made so far, and I'm proud of it. The next map I will do will have improve lighting and hopefully triggers, if you wanna teach me how to do those properly that would be amazing! But for now, enjoy this map.
